<lb n="0678a16" ed="T"/>伽陀隷<note place="inline">三</note>　摩<choice><corr>懵</corr><sic>瞢</sic></choice>呿復闍摩那迦留尼迦<note place="inline">四</note>　真陀
<lb n="0678a17" ed="T"/>摩尼富羅栘迦留尼迦<note place="inline">五</note>　薩婆阿奢彌咃𠱀栘
<lb n="0678a18" ed="T"/><note place="inline">六</note>　陀潰陀利<note place="inline">七</note>　破仇破仇<note place="inline">八</note>　留坻脾脾伽仇<note place="inline">九</note>　儨
